-- China Approves 5.6 Gigawatts of Hydropower Projects in Sichuan Province
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-11-29T08:40:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-29/china-approves-5-6-gigawatts-of-hydropower-projects-in-sichuan-province.html
China’s National Development and
Reform Commission has approved three hydropower projects in
Sichuan province, according to a statement posted on the top
economic planner’s website today. The projects have a combined
output capacity of 5.6 gigawatts, the NDRC said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ying Wang in Beijing at 
